title: A doughnut and a grilled cheese made a baby and it’s delicious | New York Post
text: 0:45 A doughnut and a grilled cheese made a baby and it’s delicious “The Flamin’ Hot Doughnut Grilled Cheese” has arrived. This savory snack is the collaboration of The Doughnut Project bakery and Clinton Hall, a trendy bar located in New York’s Financial District. The cheesy concoction is served Friday through Sunday as part of a month-long promotion. 1:28 This woman is auctioning off her virginity... for a million dollars Katherine Stone is a 21-year-old woman working at a brothel in Nevada who happens to be a virgin. In an effort to capitalize on her situation, she's decided to auction off the opportunity to deflower her, as long as the price is right. Her ideal price, a cool million dollars. 0:59 White girls are mad about finding out that 'Becky' is insulting Everyone was shocked when Iggy Azalea revealed that "Becky" is actually an insulting term for white women. This was news to everybody, especially white girls.
